dct_title_s: Plan de Tunis = Map of Tunis
dct_description_sm: Panel title. Inset: [Tunis region]. On verso: [La Médina de Tunis] -- Site archéologique de Carthage = [The Medina of Tunis] -- Archeological site of Carthage. Includes index of streets; description of Tunis, its suburbs, and the Medina.
